Sentencas: RuO2/YSZ (8% Y2O3 stabilized ZrO2)-based material was evaluated for SOFC cathodes.
Titulo: THICK-FILM RUTHENIUM OXIDE YTTRIA-STABILIZED ZIRCONIA-BASED CATHODE MATERIAL FOR SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELLS

Sentencas: Subsolidus phase equilibria in the binary RuO2-ZrO2 system and ternary RuO2-ZrO2-y2O3 system were studied.
Titulo: THICK-FILM RUTHENIUM OXIDE YTTRIA-STABILIZED ZIRCONIA-BASED CATHODE MATERIAL FOR SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELLS

Sentencas: No binary compound or solid solution exists between RuO2 and ZrO2, Which indicates the stability of the electrical and microstructural characteristics at ''working'' temperatures of SOFCs.
Titulo: THICK-FILM RUTHENIUM OXIDE YTTRIA-STABILIZED ZIRCONIA-BASED CATHODE MATERIAL FOR SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELLS

Sentencas: Thick film electrodes, printed and fired on YSZ electrolyte, exhibited usable characteristics, i.e. a porous microstructure, good adhesion and compatibility with the YSZ substrate, low sheet resistivity and a positive temperature coefficient of resistivity.
Titulo: THICK-FILM RUTHENIUM OXIDE YTTRIA-STABILIZED ZIRCONIA-BASED CATHODE MATERIAL FOR SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELLS
